data.text:
Princess Evangile is a casual game developed by MOONSTONE. It was originally released in 2015. MangaGamer published the game. Most rawgers rated the game as "Exceptional". You can play Princess Evangile on PC. The game is sold via GOG.

Negligee: Love Stories is an indie adventure game developed by Dharker Studio. It came out on 08-02-2019. It was published by Dharker Studio. Negligee: Love Stories is available on PC, macOS and Linux. You can purchase the game on Steam.

Wife Quest (2018) is a RPG game. It came out on 26-12-2018. Wife Quest (2018) is available on PC.

Sunrider Academy is an indie simulation game developed by Love in Space. It was originally released in 2015. Sekai Project published the game. The game is rated as "Recommended" on RAWG. You can play Sunrider Academy on PC, macOS and Linux. The game is sold via Steam and GOG.

Steamy Sextet is an indie adventure game developed by Belgerum. It came out on 13-01-2020. It was published by Belgerum. The game is rated as "Exceptional" on RAWG. You can play Steamy Sextet on PC, macOS and Linux. The game is sold via Steam.
